reviewText: Having already purchased Doo Wop 50, 51 & Rock, Rhythm & Doo Wop I thought I had the complete concerts.  Not so.  I was a little upset that there were performances missing from these disks. Having said that, the disk itself is a must for lovers of this music.  The quality and sound are excellent.  A must-have for any collector.
A little hit and miss, but mostly excellent.  Hank Ballard, Little Richard, the Tokens, and the Dells stand out as simply terrific.  If you have the series, this is a must.
